# Landmark papers — {{condition_name}}

Verified anchor citations for the project. Every entry must be round-tripped (PMID resolves; abstract verified verbatim) and have a corresponding `literature/papers/{PMID}.md` paper note with a quote bank.

## Format

```
### [Brief description]

- **PMID:** {pmid}
- **Year:** {year}
- **Tag:** [tag] applicability: {high / moderate / low / unknown — note}
- **One-line significance:** ...
```

## Required minimum for frontier-scan completion

At least 5 landmark papers, covering: phenotype/diagnostic-criteria source, response-definition source, adequate-trial-benchmark source, standard-of-care-ladder source, and one refractory-population cohort source. Additional landmarks accumulate as the project runs.

